[{"title":"討論 Docker 的環境問題","url":"/2023/07/14/2023-kernel-and-docker/","content":"<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p>由於自己製作的linux系統沒有apt源，我習慣用dpkg管理器（我真的不想用rpm，我知道有人會想安裝 <code>debian-archive-keyring</code>​ 來bypass掉apt的警告），但也無法使用debian的源。</p>\n<p>這是因爲在編譯的時候使用另一個源來編譯軟件，編譯好的軟件製作成deb包本身就和debian官方源相差很多，而且系統裏面的程序都是通過源碼編譯的，如果使用debian源使用在dpkg安裝的包時候會覆蓋掉一些配置文件，直接造成系統潰掉（因爲我也好奇可不可以使用官方源，所以我一個通宵都在它）</p>\n<p>換句話説就是說我製作的linux系統能跑，但是裏面的軟件需要自己編譯，所以我就在想可不可以製作一個docker環境，這樣可玩性就更多了。如果實在不行就用chroot安裝好了（但是這樣又回歸到了爲什麽不直接用debian系統的問題）。</p>\n<h2 id=\"内核配置參考\"><a href=\"#内核配置參考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内核配置參考\"></a>内核配置參考</h2><p>首先<a href=\"https://blog.hypriot.com/post/verify-kernel-container-compatibility/\">參考這篇</a>，他大致會告訴正確的docker環境是怎樣的，起碼有一個大概的方向才知道如何去建立好環境。</p>\n<p>因爲ARM架構和X86架構有點區別，於是我用ubuntu和樹莓派在兩個環境下運行了 <code>check-config.sh</code>​，并且觀察他的輸出，如下。</p>\n<h3 id=\"正常版-X64-ubuntu-内核配置：\"><a href=\"#正常版-X64-ubuntu-内核配置：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"正常版 X64 ubuntu 内核配置：\"></a>正常版 X64 ubuntu 内核配置：</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Generally Necessary:</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 全部都是 <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span>，省略掉了</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Optional Features:</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">- CONFIG_MEMCG_SWAP: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">    (cgroup swap accounting is currently enabled)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - <span class=\"string\">&quot;zfs&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - /dev/zfs: present</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - zfs <span class=\"built_in\">command</span>: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - zpool <span class=\"built_in\">command</span>: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Limits:</span><br><span class=\"line\">- /proc/sys/kernel/keys/root_maxkeys: 1000000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"ARM-樹莓派原生系統\"><a href=\"#ARM-樹莓派原生系統\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ARM 樹莓派原生系統\"></a>ARM 樹莓派原生系統</h3><p>手上的樹莓派可以執行docker，所以我就嘗試登錄ssh去拿内核配置（這是沒有魔改過原生的内核）：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Generally Necessary:</span><br><span class=\"line\">- cgroup hierarchy: cgroupv2</span><br><span class=\"line\">  Controllers:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - cpu: available</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - cpuset: available</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - io: available</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - memory: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - pids: available</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Optional Features:</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">- CONFIG_MEMCG_SWAP: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">    (cgroup swap accounting is currently enabled)</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">- CONFIG_CGROUP_HUGETLB: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">- CONFIG_SECURITY_SELINUX: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">- Network Drivers:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - <span class=\"string\">&quot;overlay&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - CONFIG_VXLAN: enabled (as module)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - CONFIG_BRIDGE_VLAN_FILTERING: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">// ............ <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> ..............</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - <span class=\"string\">&quot;zfs&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - /dev/zfs: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - zfs <span class=\"built_in\">command</span>: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - zpool <span class=\"built_in\">command</span>: missing</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Limits:</span><br><span class=\"line\">- /proc/sys/kernel/keys/root_maxkeys: 1000000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>從樹莓派的配置中可以看到大部分還是enabled的，因爲樹莓派本身不是很注重安全，所以默認沒有開啓SELINUX也是合情合理。</p>\n<p>在樹莓派中的配置文件可以看到即使 <code>CONFIG_BRIDGE_VLAN_FILTERING</code>​ missing了也可以正常使用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"標準的内核編譯\"><a href=\"#標準的内核編譯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"標準的内核編譯\"></a>標準的内核編譯</h2><p>那麽我自己編譯的内核是怎樣的呢？？</p>\n<p>​<img src=\"https://files.manesec.com/file/maneimg1/2023/06/29_docker/image-20230629123136-ojho6qu.png\" alt=\"image\">​</p>\n<p>可以看到默認的内核是不支持的，只是發行版默認編譯好了而已。</p>\n<p>也就是說如果運行自己製作的linux系統，就會一片通紅，因爲在編譯的時候，内核沒有正常開啓，所以就會導致docker跑不起來。</p>\n<p>​<img src=\"https://files.manesec.com/file/maneimg1/2023/06/29_docker/image-20230629123307-122ajpc.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>要讓docker可以在編譯後的内核跑起來，首先導出當前内核的默認配置，然後參考 <a href=\"https://github.com/lgirdk/meta-virtualization/blob/master/recipes-kernel/linux/linux-yocto\">meta-virtualization</a> 整合所有cfg文件，寫個程序把他N變成Y或者M。</p>\n<p>有沒有比較方便的方法？ 有，其實可以直接引用 <code>meta-virtualization</code>​ 然後修改bblayout和local就可以了，但不是該文章討論之内。</p>\n<p>​<img src=\"https://files.manesec.com/file/maneimg1/2023/06/29_docker/image-20230629124804-sa800kx.png\" alt=\"image\">​</p>\n<p>再一次編譯内核等待30分鐘后，裝載所有的依賴包之後，重新檢查一次就會像下面一樣。</p>\n<p>​<img src=\"https://files.manesec.com/file/maneimg1/2023/06/29_docker/image-20230629120134-fld7wb2.png\" alt=\"image\">​</p>\n<p>即使我的内核不支持 <code>CONFIG_NETFILTER_XT_MATCH_IPVS</code>​，也可以順利的跑起來，看下圖。</p>\n<p>有人説 <code>menuconfig</code>​沒有該選項，編譯kernel之前加進去編譯後也可以用，再上圖編譯後的結果看來，并不行。</p>\n<p>​<img src=\"https://files.manesec.com/file/maneimg1/2023/06/29_docker/image-20230629120204-bwkx43t.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>不過現在它可以正常的運行docker，雖然有些功能是有問題的，但是需要測試。</p>\n<p>​<img src=\"https://files.manesec.com/file/maneimg1/2023/06/29_docker/image-20230629120956-n0orknu.png\" alt=\"image\"> </p>\n<h2 id=\"結束\"><a href=\"#結束\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"結束\"></a>結束</h2><p>我製作的linux版本有ARM和X64，X64已經測試過了，ARM的buildx還遇到一些麻煩，正在處理中。</p>\n<p>‍</p>\n","tags":["docker"]},{"title":"test","url":"/2023/07/14/test/","content":"<hr>\n<p><strong>Advertisement :)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://nodeca.github.io/pica/demo/\">pica</a></strong> - high quality and fast image<br>resize in browser.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/nodeca/babelfish/\">babelfish</a></strong> - developer friendly<br>i18n with plurals support and easy syntax.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You will like those projects!</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"h1-Heading-8\"><a href=\"#h1-Heading-8\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"h1 Heading 8-)\"></a>h1 Heading 8-)</h1><h2 id=\"h2-Heading\"><a href=\"#h2-Heading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"h2 Heading\"></a>h2 Heading</h2><h3 id=\"h3-Heading\"><a href=\"#h3-Heading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"h3 Heading\"></a>h3 Heading</h3><h4 id=\"h4-Heading\"><a href=\"#h4-Heading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"h4 Heading\"></a>h4 Heading</h4><h5 id=\"h5-Heading\"><a href=\"#h5-Heading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"h5 Heading\"></a>h5 Heading</h5><h6 id=\"h6-Heading\"><a href=\"#h6-Heading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"h6 Heading\"></a>h6 Heading</h6><h2 id=\"Horizontal-Rules\"><a href=\"#Horizontal-Rules\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Horizontal Rules\"></a>Horizontal Rules</h2><hr>\n<hr>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Typographic-replacements\"><a href=\"#Typographic-replacements\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Typographic replacements\"></a>Typographic replacements</h2><p>Enable typographer option to see result.</p>\n<p>(c) (C) (r) (R) (tm) (TM) (p) (P) +-</p>\n<p>test.. test… test….. test?….. test!….</p>\n<p>!!!!!! ???? ,,  – —</p>\n<p>“Smartypants, double quotes” and ‘single quotes’</p>\n<h2 id=\"Emphasis\"><a href=\"#Emphasis\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Emphasis\"></a>Emphasis</h2><p><strong>This is bold text</strong></p>\n<p><strong>This is bold text</strong></p>\n<p><em>This is italic text</em></p>\n<p><em>This is italic text</em></p>\n<p><del>Strikethrough</del></p>\n<h2 id=\"Blockquotes\"><a href=\"#Blockquotes\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Blockquotes\"></a>Blockquotes</h2><blockquote>\n<p>Blockquotes can also be nested…</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>…by using additional greater-than signs right next to each other…</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>…or with spaces between arrows.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Lists\"><a href=\"#Lists\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Lists\"></a>Lists</h2><p>Unordered</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a list by starting a line with <code>+</code>, <code>-</code>, or <code>*</code></li>\n<li>Sub-lists are made by indenting 2 spaces:<ul>\n<li>Marker character change forces new list start:<ul>\n<li>Ac tristique libero volutpat at</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Facilisis in pretium nisl aliquet</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Nulla volutpat aliquam velit</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Very easy!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ordered</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Consectetur adipiscing elit</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Integer molestie lorem at massa</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>You can use sequential numbers…</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>…or keep all the numbers as <code>1.</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Start numbering with offset:</p>\n<ol start=\"57\">\n<li>foo</li>\n<li>bar</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"Code\"><a href=\"#Code\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Code\"></a>Code</h2><p>Inline <code>code</code></p>\n<p>Indented code</p>\n<pre><code>// Some comments\nline 1 of code\nline 2 of code\nline 3 of code\n</code></pre>\n<p>Block code “fences”</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Sample text here...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>Syntax highlighting</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> foo = <span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">bar</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> bar++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"title function_\">foo</span>(<span class=\"number\">5</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Tables\"><a href=\"#Tables\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tables\"></a>Tables</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>data</td>\n<td>path to data files to supply the data that will be passed into templates.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>engine</td>\n<td>engine to be used for processing templates. Handlebars is the default.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>ext</td>\n<td>extension to be used for dest files.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>Right aligned columns</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Option</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"right\">data</td>\n<td align=\"right\">path to data files to supply the data that will be passed into templates.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">engine</td>\n<td align=\"right\">engine to be used for processing templates. Handlebars is the default.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">ext</td>\n<td align=\"right\">extension to be used for dest files.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"Links\"><a href=\"#Links\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Links\"></a>Links</h2><p><a href=\"http://dev.nodeca.com/\">link text</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://nodeca.github.io/pica/demo/\" title=\"title text!\">link with title</a></p>\n<p>Autoconverted link <a href=\"https://github.com/nodeca/pica\">https://github.com/nodeca/pica</a> (enable linkify to see)</p>\n<h2 id=\"Images\"><a href=\"#Images\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Images\"></a>Images</h2><p><img src=\"https://octodex.github.com/images/minion.png\" alt=\"Minion\"><br><img src=\"https://octodex.github.com/images/stormtroopocat.jpg\" alt=\"Stormtroopocat\" title=\"The Stormtroopocat\"></p>\n<p>Like links, Images also have a footnote style syntax</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://octodex.github.com/images/dojocat.jpg\" alt=\"Alt text\" title=\"The Dojocat\"></p>\n<p>With a reference later in the document defining the URL location:</p>\n<h2 id=\"Plugins\"><a href=\"#Plugins\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Plugins\"></a>Plugins</h2><p>The killer feature of <code>markdown-it</code> is very effective support of<br><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.org/browse/keyword/markdown-it-plugin\">syntax plugins</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"Emojies\"><a href=\"#Emojies\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Emojies\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-emoji\">Emojies</a></h3><blockquote>\n<p>Classic markup: :wink: :crush: :cry: :tear: :laughing: :yum:</p>\n<p>Shortcuts (emoticons): :-) :-( 8-) ;)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>see <a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-emoji#change-output\">how to change output</a> with twemoji.</p>\n<h3 id=\"Subscript-x2F-Superscript\"><a href=\"#Subscript-x2F-Superscript\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Subscript &#x2F; Superscript\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-sub\">Subscript</a> &#x2F; <a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-sup\">Superscript</a></h3><ul>\n<li>19^th^</li>\n<li>H<del>2</del>O</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"lt-ins-gt\"><a href=\"#lt-ins-gt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"&lt;ins&gt;\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-ins\">&lt;ins&gt;</a></h3><p>++Inserted text++</p>\n<h3 id=\"lt-mark-gt\"><a href=\"#lt-mark-gt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"&lt;mark&gt;\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-mark\">&lt;mark&gt;</a></h3><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;Marked text&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>\n<h3 id=\"Footnotes\"><a href=\"#Footnotes\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Footnotes\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-footnote\">Footnotes</a></h3><p>Footnote 1 link[^first].</p>\n<p>Footnote 2 link[^second].</p>\n<p>Inline footnote^[Text of inline footnote] definition.</p>\n<p>Duplicated footnote reference[^second].</p>\n<p>[^first]: Footnote <strong>can have markup</strong></p>\n<pre><code>and multiple paragraphs.\n</code></pre>\n<p>[^second]: Footnote text.</p>\n<h3 id=\"Definition-lists\"><a href=\"#Definition-lists\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Definition lists\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-deflist\">Definition lists</a></h3><p>Term 1</p>\n<p>:   Definition 1<br>with lazy continuation.</p>\n<p>Term 2 with <em>inline markup</em></p>\n<p>:   Definition 2</p>\n<pre><code>    &#123; some code, part of Definition 2 &#125;\n\nThird paragraph of definition 2.\n</code></pre>\n<p><em>Compact style:</em></p>\n<p>Term 1<br>  ~ Definition 1</p>\n<p>Term 2<br>  ~ Definition 2a<br>  ~ Definition 2b</p>\n<h3 id=\"Abbreviations\"><a href=\"#Abbreviations\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Abbreviations\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-abbr\">Abbreviations</a></h3><p>This is HTML abbreviation example.</p>\n<p>It converts “HTML”, but keep intact partial entries like “xxxHTMLyyy” and so on.</p>\n<p>*[HTML]: Hyper Text Markup Language</p>\n<h3 id=\"Custom-containers\"><a href=\"#Custom-containers\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Custom containers\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-container\">Custom containers</a></h3><p>::: warning<br><em>here be dragons</em><br>:::</p>\n"}]